                <h4>上半部分</h4><div class="text-center"><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="290" height="450" src="https://indienova.com/widget/indie-game-news/guide20-0120-0126-part-1/"></iframe></div><h4>QT</h4><p>关键字：可爱、试验性</p><p>发行日期：2020/01（暂无中文）</p><p><em>QT</em> 是一个分成三部分的游戏，玩家要在在可爱的地方闲逛并找到您喜欢的朋友 ·◡·</p><p>这是给喜欢尝试非传统游戏类型玩家们玩的游戏。</p><p>详细时间待定，应该不会跳票，<a href="https://happysnakegames.itch.io/qt">itch 已经有免费版</a></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-QT55842b.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-qt-155905R.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-qt-25594Yh.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1182830/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Rover Mechanic Simulator</h4><p>关键字：模拟、建造、沙盒、太空、物理、自动化</p><p>发行日期：2020/01/23（<strong>中文支持</strong>）EA</p><p>在 <em>Rover Mechanic Simulator</em> 中， 玩家将扮演第一个火星殖民地的机械师。您的任务包括火星探测车的维修和维护，以便其余船员可以使用它们收集有关行星结构的详细信息。</p><p>使用许多设备把漫游车的最小部分拆卸。使用不同的工具，如螺丝刀，压缩机，烙铁，3D 打印机等等。在游戏的后期阶段，您将能够升级您的设备，使您的工作更加愉快和有效。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-FixENG6673WA.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-Mechanic-16738OL.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-Mechanic-26742Va.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/864680/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>TaniNani</h4><p>关键字：解谜、可爱</p><p>发行日期：2020/01/24（<strong>中文支持</strong>）</p><p>用适合你自己的节奏探索一段独特的解谜体验，<em>TaniNani</em> 是一款玩家通过控制和移动关卡构造来进行的解谜游戏，你的目的是帮助游戏中的角色找到水晶和与彼此碰面。</p><p>游戏有着 120 个精心手工制作的关卡。</p><p>话说同类游戏也已经见过好几款啦。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-TaniNani_Steam_27009ED.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-TaniNani_Steam_37015HS.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-TaniNani-17021C8.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-TaniNani-27027Hq.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1196800/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Dungeon Origins</h4><p>关键字：休闲、塌方、建设</p><p>发行日期：2020/01/24（暂无中文）</p><p>王国背叛了英雄，于是他开始寻求复仇，成为新的地牢大师！ 建立和管理地牢，突袭村庄，解锁新的进化能力，壮大强大的怪物大军，然后完成对王国的复仇！</p><p>这是一个自行建设地牢，然后努力干掉所有来寻求名利的英雄的游戏。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-BattleGif77402H.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-dungeon-17746pH.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-dungeon-27751ZR.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1220120/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>HellScape: Two Brothers</h4><p>关键字：冒险、解谜、剧情丰富</p><p>发行日期：2020/01/24（暂无中文）</p><p><em>HellScape: Two Brothers</em> 是一款强调氛围的 3D 冒险游戏。</p><p>受但丁的《神曲》启发，讲述了穿越地狱的旅程。两个兄弟为了解救被恶魔仆人绑架的妹妹，展开了艰辛的旅途。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-HellScape8776TT.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-HellScape-18785Ii.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-HellScape-28790vL.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1218090/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Dark Zone</h4><p>关键字：动作、冒险、困难</p><p>发行日期：2020/01/24（暂无中文）</p><p><em>Dark Zone</em> 是一款实时战术 RPG 游戏，您必须经过严格的试炼并赢得与敌人的最终战斗。</p><p>游戏方式还是通常的在牢房中移动，拾起武器，护甲和治疗药水，与敌人作战。</p><p>游戏由 4 个地区组成，每个地区都有必须要战胜的守护者。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-DarkZone930210.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-DarkZone-193118l.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-DarkZone-29336wN.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1220910/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Olaguna Chronicles（命运启示录 -阿尔巴雷克战纪-）</h4><p>关键字：角色扮演、冒险、策略、回合制</p><p>发行日期：2020/01/25（<strong>中文支持</strong>）EA</p><p>本作是款回合制 SRPG 游戏，每个关卡都有不同的目标，包括 击败、解谜、生存、逃脱等。</p><p>奥拉古纳是以奥拉古贝斯、奥拉玛威岛和罗格伊丹岛屿三大区域所组成：奥拉古纳大陆。</p><p>奥拉古纳历 338 年，巴雷克斯神罚联合发动了对领国阿尔伯瑟自由国的侵袭战，乌德纳尔率领的白银之手骑士团在纳斯卡平原战役全军覆没.....至此阿尔伯瑟与巴雷克斯长达 50 多年的攻守平衡状态被打破！奥拉古贝斯南部进入全面战争.....</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-Olaguna-19610hj.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-Olaguna-29616L2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/01/pic-Olaguna-39620Gy.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/985650/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>本周其他值得关注的游戏</h4><ul><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/846730/RUGBY_20/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">RUGBY 20</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/916840/The_Walking_Dead_Saints__Sinners/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">The Walking Dead: Saints &amp; Sinners</a><br>《行尸走肉:圣徒与罪人》VR 版</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1100420/Praetorians__HD_Remaster/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Praetorians - HD Remaster</a><br>《罗马执政官》高清重制版</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1100410/Commandos_2__HD_Remaster/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Commandos 2 - HD Remaster</a><br>《盟军敢死队 2》高清重制版</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1203980/_/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">恋 一些小清新的猎奇故事</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1209980/CaveBugBoy/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">CaveBugBoy</a><br>平台冒险</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1052640/Retrace/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Retrace 时空回溯</a><br>悬疑解谜视觉小说</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1149550/Utawarerumono_Mask_of_Deception/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">传颂之物:虚伪的假面</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1151440/Utawarerumono_Mask_of_Truth/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">传颂之物:二人的白皇</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1217070/Der_Geisterturm__The_Ghost_Tower/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Der Geisterturm / The Ghost Tower</a><br>3D 迷宫回合制策略</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/735490/__The_Dreams_of_Candlelight/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">烛梦灯 The Dreams of Candlelight</a><br>民国题材悬疑解谜</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/841070/Dominance/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Dominance</a><br>顶视角多人在线射击</li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1217190/_/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">浮世万千之前世今生</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1222160/_/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">毛笔模拟器</a></li></ul>
